import cv2
import numpy as np

imgGet = cv2.imread('./akira.jpg')

gray = cv2.cvtColor(imgGet, cv2.COLOR_RGB2GRAY)

cv2.imshow('gray', gray)

cv2.waitKey(0)
cv2.destroyAllWindows()


#ふが要望-------------

imgSize = np.shape(imgGet)

#print(imgGst), for i in imgGet いすると一部だけ出力されるので、

for i in range(imgSize[0]):
    print("[", end="")
    for j in range(imgSize[1]):
        print("[", end="")
        for k in range(imgSize[2]):
            if(k == imgSize[2]-1):
                print(imgGet[i][j][k], end="")
            else :
                print(imgGet[i][j][k], end=" ")
        print("]", end="")
    print("]")
